[thinking] **Analyzing class loading behavior**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm exploring how the generated helper might be affected by the absence of a line number and whether tracer filters impact the call stack. I wonder if `Class.forName` only gets intercepted when a class isn't already loaded. Maybe all classes are initially loaded during instrumentation? If they are, does `Class.forName` still get called without a dynamic event? It seems the native agent only logs when a class is missing, so I need to test a target external JDK class to check.
[thinking] 
