[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking that closure might be loading in a way that isn't instrumented. It could be related to how `MethodHandles.lookup().findClass` functions when it loads from instrumented contexts. I wonder if there’s a way to examine how tests for other classes handled `Class.forName`. It seems like an important aspect to consider, and I'll need to look into it to understand the situation better.
